technical sciences V. S. Kavunov--Chief of Military Academy of 
Chemical Protection, director of provisory creative team A. D. 
Zimon--doctor of technical sciences, professor M. I. 
Reznichenko--candidate of chemical sciences 
  REFERENCES 
