<H3> <TI>   Power Industry Development in Kyrgyzstan in 1993-2010 and Cooperation With CIS Countries in This Field </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  947F0044A Minsk IZVESTIYA VYSSHIKH UCHEBNYKH ZAVEDENIY: 
