  Republic of Buryatia Irkutsk Oblast Krasnoyarsk Kray 
Republic 
of Sakha (Yakutiya) Republic of Tuva Khakass Republic Chita 
Oblast 
12. Far Eastern 
  Amur Oblast Kamchatka Oblast Magadan Oblast Primorski Kray 
Sakhalin Oblast Kabarovsk Kray 


</TEXT>

