                           AH     DLP    EBW    smoking             DLP+EBW    DLP+smoking    DLP+AH    EBW+smoking    EBW+AH    smoking+AH             DLP+EBW+smoking    DLP+EBW+AH    DLP+          EBW+smoking+AH 
